de.tu_darmstadt.gdi1.gorillas.ui.widgets.valueadjuster

Class AdvancedValueAdjusterInt

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.matthiasmann.twl.Widget
      • de.tu_darmstadt.gdi1.gorillas.ui.widgets.valueadjuster.AdvancedValueAdjuster
        • de.tu_darmstadt.gdi1.gorillas.ui.widgets.valueadjuster.AdvancedValueAdjusterInt

  • public class AdvancedValueAdjusterInt
extends AdvancedValueAdjuster
    This is a slightly changed version of Matthias Mann's ValueAdjusterInt class. It just extends AdvancedValueAdjuster instead of ValueAdjuster and overrides handleEditCallback(int key). This method's body makes sure that nothing but an int bigger or equal than minValue and smaller or equal than maxValue is accepted.
    Author:
    Matthias Mann, Peter Klöckner
